description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Go is an ancient board game that involves deep thinking, strategy, and tactics. Players take turns placing their stones on a board in order to gain the most territory and capture the most enemy stones.
